{"tid":2087060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到呢度同埋Twitter嘅人開始del  account，有d感慨。","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T16:28:05.000Z","uid":356385,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27d1ac85d8774497d598781d8605529629a97632","tid":2087060,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"聽日支安法正式生效。呢一年幾來，我地真係經歷好多好多。<br />\n<br />\n最初反送中果陣，連登係最團結，最感人嘅時候。文宣，戰術，甚至遺書，都係呢度睇到，令人對呢個小小嘅forum完全改觀，登上國際舞台。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter都係，當初手足們情緒都好激動，但大家互相照顧，關心，先可以行度今日。<br />\n<br />\n民主抗爭嘅道路係漫長的。有人等唔到，有人不願意等，選擇離開，沈默，呢個可以明白。誰不害怕中共？特別當你了解黨史嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n不知道呢度仲有幾多人堅持。無論點都好，我唔會去怪佢地。<br />\n<br />\n聽日係味end game？冇人知，因為聽日之後，香港又進入新一階段，更黑暗嘅時候來臨。<br />\n<br />\n無論係點，我唔想香港人放棄。因為我地冇地回頭了。只有堅持落下，可能有希望。放棄就一定冇。我希望各位抱住呢個簡單道理。<br />\n<br />\n之後會更痛苦，選擇留底嘅人，我同你一起堅持落去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日，71，去shopping！</span>"},{"pid":"b2f5d86308052428e9cdbbcec8b458a67d780007","tid":2087060,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日好想去買嘢食！"},{"pid":"28e68c15f3c6cb6ec33d749f4f21edf02bb539a9","tid":2087060,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去食飯都要拉我？"},{"pid":"62408919aa1a33cb6de7fd0cc74098705e17c7ae","tid":2087060,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji